Championnat National 2ème Division

Four games to play: Cercle Olympique is the leader.

 
Championnat Regional de la Region de Ségou

Poule composition:

Poule A
AS Biton, AS Bakaridjan (Baraouéli), Bindugu FC (Bla).

Poule B
Renaissance (Ségou), Djonkala (Bla), AS Santoro (San).

Poule C
AS Comatex, Bronconi (Niono), AS Djaradjan (Markala), Avenir (Ségou).

Poule D
USFAS, AS Falé (Macina), AS Sofa (Molodo).

Only three rounds played; winners of each poule qualify to second stage.
Second stage played by four teams (6 rounds) and the winners are Ségou Regional Champions.



